  <brief_title>Hypoxia-based Dose Escalation With Radiochemotherapy in Head and Neck Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomized Phase II Study for Dose Escalation in Locally Advanced Head and Neck Squamous Cell Carcinomas Treated With Radiochemotherapy</official_title>
  <sponsors>
